SAML Token Notes
+---------------+

Why?
SAML token are an authorisation mechanism
Started with XBOX (Microsoft standard)

Proof a person has permission to view a clip

Person purchases SD it will stop them trying to watch HD

SAML token has VPID and how long its valid
BBC store SAML tokens last 4 hours
BBC extra is subscription based
On Test environment we can have them last as long as we want (Aimee 100 days)

Has to be https

If you stayed on page and left for 4 hours and tried to play, it would fail
